  "description": {
    "zh": "我这儿又有新订单，你要不要再帮一把？这次是两把非常独特的枪，全是美式 AK。其中一把居然用的是 .300 blackout 子弹，离谱吧？\n\n总之，我各要一把，其中一把配置要求更多。废话少说，具体规格我写给你了，明白了吗？\n\nRD-704 要求：\n - 后坐力总和小于 260\n - 重量小于 4.9 公斤\n - 人机功效 79 或更高\n - 耐久度至少 95 %\n - 宽度占用 4格 或更少\n - “射击场”距离 600米 或更多\n - Insight WMX200战术手电\n - AN/PEQ-15战术设备\n - US Palm AK手枪式握把\n - Fab Defence PDC АК-74防尘盖\n - AK 7.62x39 FAB Defense Ultimag 30R 30发容量弹匣\n\nVelociraptor 要求：\n - 后坐力总和小于 350\n - 重量小于 3.8 公斤\n - 人机功效 74 或更高\n - 耐久度至少 95 %\n - 弹匣容量 40 或更多\n - 任意 紧凑型准直式瞄具",
    "en": "So, new order, interested in lending a hand again? It's about two very unique guns. American-made AK rifles, one of them is chambered in .300 Blackout, how crazy is that?\n\nAnyway, I need one of each, one of which has more specific requirements, so I'll skip the explaining and just give you the specifics written down. You got that?\n\nRD-704 Requirements :\n - Recoil Sum less than 260\n - Weight less than 4.9 KG\n - Ergonomics 79 or higher\n - Durability higher than 95 %\n - Width of 4 slots or less\n - Sighting Range of 600 Meters or more\n - Insight WMX200 Tactical Flashlight\n - L3Harris AN/PEQ-15 Tactical Device\n - AK US Palm Pistol Grip\n - AK FAB Defense PDC Dust Cover\n - AK 7.62x39 FAB Defense Ultimag 30R 30-Round Magazine\n\nVelociraptor Requirements :\n - Recoil Sum less than 350\n - Weight less than 3.8 KG\n - Ergonomics 74 or higher\n - Durability higher than 95 %\n - Magazine Capacity of 40 or more\n - A Compact Collimator"
  },
